#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use it as standalone program to preview and install a font "
"downloaded from the Internet. In the preview you can check that the font has "
"all characters you need."
msgstr ""
"Seda võib kasutada autonoomse rakendusena internetist alla laaditud fondi "
"eelvaatluseks ja paigaldamiseks. Eelvaatluses saab kontrollida, kas fondil "
"on ikka kõik märgid, mida sul tarvis läheb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:42
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Additionally &kfontview; can be launched from the &systemsettings; module "
#| "<ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/fontinst/index.html\"> <guilabel>Font "
#| "Installer</guilabel></ulink> to use the extended preview capabilities of "
#| "&kfontview;."
msgid ""
"Additionally &kfontview; can be launched from the &systemsettings; module "
"<ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/fontinst/index.html\"> <guilabel>Font "
"Management</guilabel></ulink> to use the extended preview capabilities of "
"&kfontview;."
msgstr ""
"Lisaks saab &kfontview; käivitada Süsteemi seadistuste moodulis <ulink url="
"\"help:/kcontrol/fontinst/index.html\"><guilabel>Fontide paigaldaja</"
"guilabel></ulink>, mis lubab ära kasutada &kfontview; eelvaatluse omadusi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively you can use the <guilabel>Font Management</guilabel> module to "
"install, remove, preview and manage all fonts on your system."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kfontview; application</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kfontview; rakendus</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kfontview; application</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kfontview; rakendus</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kfontview;'s <guilabel>Standard Preview</guilabel> displays your font in "
"several different sizes using a pangram (a sentence using every letter of "
"the alphabet at least once). So you can get a good idea of what it will look "
"like. From the drop down box in the toolbar you can choose additional "
"preview types:"
msgstr ""
"&kfontview; <guilabel>standardne eelvaatlus</guilabel> näitab fonti mitmes "
"suuruses, kasutades pangrammi ehk lauset, milles kasutatakse tähestiku kõiki "
"tähti. Nii saab igakülgselt näha, milline font välja näeb. Tööriistariba "
"hüpikmenüü abil saab valida mõningaid täiendavaid eelvaatluse tüüpe:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>All Characters</guilabel> displays all characters provided by the "
"font in one size."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kõik sümbolid</guilabel> näitab kõiki fondi pakutavaid sümboleid "
"ühes suuruses."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unicode Block: The Unicode standard arranges groups of characters together "
"in blocks"
msgstr "Unicode'i plokk: Unicode'i standard korraldab märgirühmad plokkidesse"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unicode Script: In Unicode, a script is a collection of letters and other "
"written signs used to represent textual information in one or more writing "
"systems"
msgstr ""
"Unicode'i skript: Unicode'is on skript tähtede ja muude kirjamärkide kogum, "
"mis tähistab tekstiteavet ühes või rohkemas kirjasüsteemis"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Change Text</guibutton>: Using this button opens the "
"<guilabel>Preview String</guilabel> dialog where you can insert a user "
"defined text. This feature enables you to check that a font supports the "
"characters you need."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Muuda teksti</guibutton>: selle nupuga saab avada dialoogi "
"<guilabel>Eelvaatlusstring</guilabel>, kus saab määrata kindlaks teksti. See "
"võimaldab kontrollida, kas font ikka toetab märke, mida vajad."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the zoom buttons or the mousewheel to change the font size in "
"all preview types."
msgstr ""
"Fondi suurust kõigis eelvaatluse tüüpides saab muuta suurendusnuppudega või "
"hiirerattaga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <guilabel>Unicode Block</guilabel> and <guilabel>Unicode Script</"
"guilabel> preview mode additional tooltip info's are displayed hovering a "
"character with the mouse pointer: The character's Unicode "
"<guilabel>Category</guilabel> and the value in <guilabel> UCS-4</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>UTF-16</guilabel>, <guilabel>UTF-8</guilabel> and as <guilabel>XML "
"Decimal Entity</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Eelvaatluserežiimide <guilabel>Unicode'i plokk</guilabel> ja "
"<guilabel>Unicode'i skript</guilabel> korral näidatakse märgi kohal, mis "
"asub hiirekursori all, täiendavat kohtspikrit: märgi Unicode'i "
"<guilabel>kategooria</guilabel> ning väärtus <guilabel>UCS-4</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>UTF-16</guilabel>, <guilabel>UTF-8</guilabel> ja <guilabel>XML "
"kümnendolemina</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To install a font you downloaded from the Internet, click the "
"<guibutton>Install</guibutton> button in the lower-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Internetist alla laaditud fondi paigaldamiseks klõpsa all paremal asuvale "
"nupule <guibutton>Paigalda</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can install the font for personal us only available to you or system-"
"wide available for all users, the latter will require administrator "
"privileges."
msgstr ""
"Fonte saab paigaldada isiklikuks kasutamiseks, nii et need on mõeldud ainult "
"sulle, aga ka süsteemsena, nii et neid saavad kasutada kõik süsteemi "
"kasutajad. Viimasel juhul on vaja administraatori õigusi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fonts are often provided in an archive format like <literal role=\"extension"
"\">zip</literal>. Open these archives with &ark; which provides a simple "
"previewer for fonts. To make use of the extended capabilities of &kfontview; "
"extract the fonts and open them in &kfontview;."
msgstr ""
"Fonte levitatakse sageli kokkupakituna, näiteks <literal role=\"extension"
"\">zip</literal>-failina. Ava need arhiivid rakendusega &ark;, mis pakub "
"ühtlasi fontide lihtsat eelvaatlust. &kfontview; täiendavate võimaluste "
"kasutamiseks paki fondid lahti ja ava rakenduses &kfontview;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applications need to be restarted to use of the newly installed fonts."
msgstr "Paigaldatud uute fontide kasutamiseks tuleb rakendused taaskäivitada."

